reviews.text: Went there after a day of shopping, and order the lamb. Was pleasantly surprised on the overall taste of the dish. The meal came with a soup and a choice of rice or noodles. The overall experience was good, the service could have been a bit better though.

Bad quality & services.
食物差 及 服務差，連早餐咁簡單都唔掂，次次件多士都係又凍又淋；浪費食材。同老細講過都冇用，以後唔去啦 …
高層及收錢員（可能自己人）見錢都黑口黑面，低層服務可以，所以見到高層即閃
food quality good. High rental fee causing high food price. 食味不錯，商場租金貴，食物價錢亦貴。
